JSE-listed Distribution and Warehousing Network, or Dawn, has appointed Chris Booyens as its CFO and FD, effective May 1. A qualified chartered accountant, Booyens has several years&rsquo; experience in the building industry as Iliad Africa group FD. He also previously served as financial executive and executive director at Tiger Brands for more than a decade. The company&rsquo;s board welcomed Booyens, noting that it was looking forward to the contribution he would make to the company with his significant experience in listed environments and in turnaround situations.